            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Healing is the vital art of mending wounds and curing ailments, blending mundane medicine with magical restoration. Skilled healers use bandages, herbs, and potions alongside spells or divine blessings to close gashes, purge poisons, or revive the fallen. In a perilous realm of swords and monsters, this expertise is a lifeline, sustaining adventurers through brutal battles or cursed afflictions. It\u2019s the difference between life and death, wielded by clerics, medics, and alchemists alike.",
